Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am a man of sin. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A single woman comes\Nto my doorstep to woo me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A friend through long years of language\Nstudy; is it time to move beyond friendship?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have I ever been the recipient of an\Nattack by a person of such charms before?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, before my eyes is another woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She came to me from that\Nother man, and she speaks but a little.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And indeed, there is yet another woman whose\Nfeelings are wedging into a corner of my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She is, even now, waiting and\Nwaiting for me to come to her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear God! Is it a sin for\Na man to be so popular?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whatever shall I do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Outside the door is the sexy Hanuki-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the boarding house is\Nthe silent, exquisite Kaori-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And waiting at the café is my\Nyet unseen pen-pal, Keiko-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unless I plan on becoming a\NRenaissance man of the sexual arts,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must narrow it down to one of them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.87,0:01:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose Keiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will not succumb to the flesh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I should do now is strip away all\Nveneer and reveal myself as I am at this moment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiko-san, please wait for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:33.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tatami Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I was a brand-spanking\Nnew freshman university student{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and before my eyes were open innumerable\Ndoors to that rose-colored campus life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, devoting my life to a single circle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}poses a chance of wasting\Nmy entire college life in vain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One must spread out the risk. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will join many circles and experience\Na diversified rose-colored campus life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I have always been of the indoor persuasion,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will search for encounters through reading!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading Circle Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Books are the ocean! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now is the time to set sail\Non the sea of the printed word!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The waves of life, the wind, the sad rain,\Nthe storm of trials, the hopeless Sargasso...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The meetings and partings\Nof a submergent coastline! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The morning sun of hope... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, one day, I encounter a single small ship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And on that ship is a raven-haired maiden...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's quiet. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reading is, after all, a solitary journey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think this is a little too quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seeds of love can't sprout here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alone adrift on the Pacific!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appreciate the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:20.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night is Brief, Go Forth Maidens
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a silly little young-adult novel,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but feel free to use it as\Na bad example to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He said he'd bought it at a used book store\Nand didn't need it anymore, so I should read it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Its content was that of a\Nsilly little young-adult novel,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but on the final page was an address\Nand name, written in exquisite penmanship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seemed to be the name of the previous owner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I become strangely curious\Nabout this "Higuchi Keiko" person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had long been envious of those\Nengaging in the exchange of letters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dreamer in me itched to\Ntrade carefully crafted correspondence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if, by some unforeseen chance,\Nan opportunity should arise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I'd expressed this\Nwish to Ozu in the past...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be exciting to send off lewd\Nprose to a woman you don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a hopeless deviant.\NWhat am I to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ribald writing wretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is how he called me a giant pervert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I saw it as an excellent chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is not this, indeed, the command of heaven?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is not forming a pen-pal relationship with an\Nunseen woman a once in a lifetime opportunity?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But sending off a letter unannounced is at\Nthe very least unrefined, or simply freakish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so I purchased\Nstationery that was beautiful,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to make up for that freakishness\Noverflowing with sincerity,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and wrote a letter\Ncontaining harmless pleasantries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First I apologized profusely\Nfor sending a letter uninvited,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then added a note explaining\Nhow I was a hardworking student,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and, neither praising nor criticizing, gave\Nmy impressions of the novel I'd finished.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wrote nothing of requesting\Nto receive a response.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a lengthy missive would\Ngive off a somewhat freakish vibe,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wrote revision after revision,\Naiming for a mere half a page.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It requires considerable\Nresolve to send a reply to a letter{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that was sent to you from an unknown\Nperson in this world of corrupt morals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even more if it's some maiden\Nraised among butterflies and rainbows.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was prepared to not feel\Nhurt if a response did not come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear you, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you for the letter. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Through this letter\NI could tell from her modesty{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that Keiko-san was herself\Na lovely raven-haired maiden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bingo! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, from such an unbelievably simple start,\Nmy two years exchanging letters had begun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The hot and humid days continue on, like summer\Nis coming just a step ahead, don't you think?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In my boarding house there is quite\Npoor ventilation, so it is considerably hot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It became quite humid after\Nthe hollyhock festival ended, yes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before the rainy season comes, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a sense we've entered\Nthe doldrums of summer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think being able to study whatever\Nyou'd like in college is a really amazing thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you researching in your studies there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:07:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My research is nothing particularly\Nspecial... I am majoring in agriculture.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am deeply interested in the world of science.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I feel it a shame that one is not\Nable to survey all of this broad field.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such progress is what enables our modern\Nway of life, however, so I cannot complain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It sounds like your studies\N are quite wonderful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for me, a lecturer that has been in Japan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for three years was returning\N to his home country,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and we threw a farewell party\Nat an Irish pub on Oike street.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't drink, but the fried\Nwhitefish was very delicious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have never been to an Irish pub\Nbefore, but I do wish to go one day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have much interest in the culture of England.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope to one day go there myself and\Ntest out the fruits of my language study.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to my father's work, I spent a\Nshort time in New York during my childhood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was raised greatly admiring Miles Davis and\NMagic Johnson (has it already been so long?),{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I remember skating there. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I use that experience to teach at an\Ninter-college English conversation circle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like my experience might be of\Nsome small help to the other students.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you've lived overseas?\NI think that's really amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if you strain yourself with studying\Ntoo much, it's not good for your health.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be careful not to overdo it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you for your concern. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As you say, I am also engaging\Nin what physical activity I may.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, as a way to relieve stress\NI enjoy playing the part of an action star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know it's childish and laughable,\Nbut it is a "hero" TV show!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It gives me a chance to train\Nmy body, and at the same time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can let children live their dreams!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is a job worth doing, indeed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish to teach children\Nthat justice will prevail!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, save Mochiguman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bad guys are trying\Nto kidnap the girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, make them change their ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change your ways! Change\Nyour ways! Change your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change your ways! Change your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, they ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mochiguman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think he's some freak?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It sounds like a wonderful activity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I also love heroes that make children happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although I, too, am\Nembarrassed by my childish taste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the letters came from Keiko-san,\Nso too did my glimpses at her personality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was, indeed, my ideal woman!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wrote about myself, trying\Nto be as appealing as possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although there were\Nsome slight embellishments,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they were all for the sake\Nof classy presentation, yes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been beaming lately.\NSomething happen of note?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of note or notes, it's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are exchanging letters with a\Nmystery woman you've never met, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I hit the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, doing it by exchanging letters is\Nprobably perfect for a spineless wimp like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not doing these rude things you think I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, I know you.\NYou're made half out of porn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now you're anguishing\Nover wanting to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't be able to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a platonic relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Said I, while at the same time being in\Na close relationship with two other girls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just go with your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hanuki-san's English was left\Na bit too much to her feelings;{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she was a miraculous master of soul talk that\Nexpressed herself perfectly to the instructor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you and Ozu-{\i1}kun {\i0}are in the same year?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a small world, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a patient at our practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to his meddling\NI've gotten into a ton of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it. That's his hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he has a habit of keeping\Nsecrets about himself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know where he lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't tell me no matter how much I ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's in Joudoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little ways off of Shirakawa\Nroad is an apartment building
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that looks like it's made of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Ozu-{\i1}kun {\i0}gets a\Nlot of money from his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can he piss me off any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hanuki-san, who I was\Nhaving frank conversation with,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is an lovely older dental hygienist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We started going to a café together after class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, because of the Hero Show,\NI came to take care of a certain woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori is a very elegant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be very courteous to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go thinking anything weird, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to Mr. Jougasaki who hired me,\NI was exceedingly cautious and a safe bet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her hair was carefully combed,\Nand her clothes were elegant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't think of her as a doll at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not like I couldn't understand\Nhow Mr. Jougasaki could be{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so enthralled with this beauty. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu-{\i1}kun{\i0} doesn't drink, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It causes problems, so I only\Ndrink with people I'm close to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need a drinking buddy,\NI'd be happy to, anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so easy to handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone she's close to, huh?\NI haven't entered that category yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, one day Hanuki-{\i1}san {\i0}and I will drain\Na barrel of Yamazaki distillery whiskey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, your place stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His enemy in the longstanding\NMasochistic Proxy-Proxy War
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had infiltrated Mr. Jougasaki's\Nboarding house, and with hidden cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,filmed scenes of him caring for his\Ndear Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}, and screened an exposé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure you've got the\Nballs for it, but my place isn't safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on to Kaori here\Nfor a little while, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, I'm sorry. I know this is a filthy\Nplace, but please endure it for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suddenly we began living together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The game of Love had taken such a sudden turn,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but my letters with Keiko-san\Nalso continued unabated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are two crucial points\Nabout exchanging letters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first is that they must be handwritten.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the second is that you never\Nmeet your partner in correspondence,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even should the very\Ncauldron of hell be unleashed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the world come to an end. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Says I, but it is only human to\Nbecome curious about your partner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is she like? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What does she wear? What is her home like?\NHow does she walk? What does she look like?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to know more! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One time only, I headed toward her address.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was impulsive. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,White Garden Joudoji 306
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,White Garden Joudoji
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wasn't that Akashi-san?\NI wonder if she recognized me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akashi-san was in the class one year below me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}together with Ozu \Nin the engineering department.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had always wanted to question why she\Nended up hanging out with a person like him{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and visiting a person on the second floor\Nof Shimogamo Yuusuisou they call "Master."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, I had thought I would continue\Nmy platonic relationship with Keiko-san, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Greetings. Spring sure is in full bloom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:14:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's already been two years since we\Nstarted this back-and-forth of letters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is something I want to say...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could we meet up, face to face, one time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I surely caught her fancy\Nthrough my genius literary skills.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am entirely a man of sin. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I could not meet her. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The me in the letters had walked\Nfar away from the me in reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had originally written the\Nhigh expectations of myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd predicted would be true\Nby the time I met Keiko-san,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but at some point it had\Nbecome pure fabrication.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I cannot disillusion Keiko-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have lied far too much. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't show my face to her. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she gathered the courage\Nand wrote "I want to see you!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I, a man, doing being so indecisive?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's still not too late! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll become the me that's in the letters!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll become a man worthy of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, the hurdles were far too high.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did I even write those\Nthings in the letters to begin with?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiko-san kept repeating the\Ninvitation, and I kept dodging the issue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna go out for some drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was finally asked out\Nfor a drink by Hanuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This certifies that she feels close to me now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a report I need to write today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Good luck on your report!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can wait no longer. I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting at the Café Collection \Non August 13 at 8 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If perchance you do not come, let us no longer\Npersist in this exchange of letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That meeting is tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But today is my last day with Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day Mr. Jougasaki came\Nto say he was taking Kaori-{\i1}san {\i0}back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are being torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you'll forget about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was being forced into making a\Ndecision about all three women at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I think about the past two years,\Nwhat a sweet, innocent two years I've led.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that it's finally come to this,\NI must head toward moving past this climax!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do I go for drinks with Hanuki-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do I take Kaori-san and run away?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do I meet Keiko-san and\Nreveal the whole truth to her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unless I plan to become a\NRenaissance man of the sexual arts,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must narrow it down to one of them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if it's like this, I'd rather have\Nsome guy that asks me out every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had a sinking feeling that she was falling\Ninto the clutches of that perverted dentist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-{\i1}san {\i0}must have wanted moral support!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let her be ruined by the\Ninvitations of the perverted dentist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a matter of life and death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot stand idly by and watch it unfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First thing: Consult the old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 6000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:31.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Went to lounge, drinking contest\Nwith Jougasaki, a tough battle but won,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,then dragged around by Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, ended\Nup at her apartment, but with a 'Keiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!!'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:35.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran out of her bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind!\NI'll show her my true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Searching for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you! Didn't I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opportunity is always\N dangling before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Surcharge: 6000 yen + 2000 yen = 8000 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her apartment! You have to\Nsurprise her at her apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Visiting the home of your\Npen-pal is completely unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's breaking the most fundamental rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rules are made to be broken. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiko-san lives up there in room 306.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am going to show Keiko-san\Nthe real me if it's the last thing I do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was then that I saw Keiko-san\Nwith an extremely eerie face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With an unhealthy looking face\Nthat seemed like it belonged to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a human from the dark side of the moon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An ominous smile rising up that seemed\Nlike it was entreating others' misery...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd say it was strangely\Nslippery, like some youkai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She almost looked like Ozu. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She and Ozu were two peas in a pod.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or rather, she was exactly like Ozu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, that is Ozu! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Swallowing the conclusion I had come to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within my mind required a great\Namount of effort from my soul.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I needed a whole cupful of sugar to make\Nthis unimaginably bitter medicine go down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Higuchi Keiko did not exist. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,An apartment building \Nthat looks like it's made of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had been exchanging letters\Nwith Ozu these past two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could there be a more cruel conclusion?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}! It's you, right {\i1}Senpai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for deceiving you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, but I participated\Nin the exchange of letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote the letters at\Nthe request of Ozu-{\i1}senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I felt pained from these actions,\NI could not bring myself to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so it was you, Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ozu is the only one at fault, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Ozu-{\i1}senpai {\i0}got bored with it after a\Nwhile... It was just a random prank to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could not bring myself to simply fade out,\Nso I took over writing the letters as Keiko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite difficult capturing\NKeiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s character.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Ozu-{\i1}senpai {\i0}\Nknew your tastes extremely well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and had used them to create the character.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. Keiko-{\i1}san {\i0}was my ideal\Nwoman, far too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to think that it was Ozu who created her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you didn't come to where I said to meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might stop\Nby here, so I staked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was saved by you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the Mochiguman Show?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was still in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were\Nreally cool back then, {\i1}Senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was me while I was in the suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a lot of fun exchanging letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true you like to show off a little,\Nbut I was lying as well, so we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These come in sets of five,\Nbut I lost one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love Mochiguman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of embarrassing, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opportunity is always dangling\N before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:51.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,- I collected Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}. \NThe castella is a reward from Jougasaki-{\i1}san{\i0}.\N- Ozu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you go straight home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a pretty nice moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you at least ask her out on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-{\i1}san {\i0}just likes Mochiguman, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I'm tearin' outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I think about it, enough Keiko-san,\Nenough Hanuki-san or Kaori-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be that I was just\Ndancing in the palm of Ozu's hand?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That goddamn monster, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}eating the unhappiness of others as\Na topping on his three helpings of rice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that I think about it, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he must have had quite a delicious\Nfeast from me these past two years!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He deserves to die a thousand times over!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll roast him into\Ncoffee and grind him to bits!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Silently I ate the entire castella myself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and through my actions sank\Ndeeper into a hellish solitude.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I devoured the castella,\NI took on the form of a devil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right, don't misunderstand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:21:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was enamored with Keiko-san,\Nwho was created by Ozu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was most definitely not Akashi-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't change the subject. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's inexcusable to momentarily lust\Nafter someone just because you're lonely!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, it is my fate to be dragged down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}forever with Ozu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mariana Trench
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I thought that,\NI found myself strangely relieved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not suited to stand\Non love's victory podium.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is how it should be... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like hell it is! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to stand on the victory podium,\Nno matter what methods I have to use!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
